reviewText: Great Family entertainment! This movie is appropriate for all ages. A heartwarming story of family devotion, respect for traditions and the preservation of those traditions.
With all the trash on TV you can't go wrong with this collection....It brings peace to the soul....
I love Thomas Kinkade. I never knew he had more than one movie.

These movies are wonderful for the whole family. Exactly what I love about the Thomas Kinkade series! We definitely came away with the real spirit of the season and will enjoy adding this collection to our seasonal traditions.

I was not disappointed and was well pleased in receiving and watching this movie.  A family movie for all to see and understand the true meaning of family and celebrating the birth of our Lord and Savior.  You will not be disappointed in purchasing this movie collection.
My Aunt loved this and I bought another one for myself and I projected the pictures onto my walls at work at Christmas time.
This was a beautiful, heart felt movie that would bring you laughter and tears.  I saw this on Halmark channel then had to buy one for myself and one for a Christmas present.
